title: Rainbow Arch
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Caribbean, Jamaican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local, home-spun kind of place that makes plenty of vegan food using fresh ingredients. Around 1/5 of the menu is vegan suitable. The floor is beach sand, as it's right on the 7 mile beach, behind a couple of palm trees.
